          }
        },
        {
          "key": "first_meeting_high_skill",
          "value": {
            "speakerName": "Ruben",
            "text": "Your fillets have been drawing compliments from the inn's chef.\n\nEfficiency approaches artistry. Do you have work, or are you here to learn more?",
