        },
        {
          "key": "processing_tutorial_intro",
          "value": {
            "speakerName": "Ruben",
            "text": "Cassandra sent you? Good. I'm Ruben.\n\nProcessing isn't a hobby. It's a discipline. You waste less, earn more, and honor the catch.\n\nIf you're serious, I'll teach you deboning.",
            "showAsAction": true,
            "showConditions": [],
            "triggersOnShow": [],
            "choices": [
              {
                "choiceText": "I want to learn properly. I'm a stewardship student.",
                "resultDialogId": "processing_tutorial_step1",
                "triggersOnShow": [],
                "showConditions": []
              },
              {
                "choiceText": "Cassandra said it would help me earn more.",
                "resultDialogId": "processing_tutorial_step1",
                "triggersOnShow": [],
                "showConditions": []
              }
            ],
            "nextDialogId": ""
          }
        },
        {
          "key": "processing_tutorial_step1",
          "value": {
            "speakerName": "Ruben",
            "text": "Good. We'll use a common farmed tilapia. It's forgiving for learning.\n\nFirst, the tweezers. Use them for the small bones.\n\nPull gently and carefully. Every bone removed means a better product.",
            "showAsAction": true,
            "showConditions": [],
            "triggersOnShow": [],
            "choices": [
              {
                "choiceText": "What's next?",
                "resultDialogId": "processing_tutorial_step2",
                "triggersOnShow": [],
                "showConditions": []
              }
            ],
            "nextDialogId": ""
          }
        },
        {
          "key": "processing_tutorial_step2",
          "value": {
            "speakerName": "Ruben",
            "text": "Now, the knife. Follow the spine with steady, confident strokes.\n\nClean cuts mean more meat, less waste, better value.\n\nThis is where skill separates the processor from the butcher.",
            "showAsAction": true,
            "showConditions": [],
            "triggersOnShow": [],
            "choices": [
              {
                "choiceText": "What now?",
                "resultDialogId": "processing_tutorial_complete",
                "triggersOnShow": [],
                "showConditions": []
              }
            ],
            "nextDialogId": ""
          }
        },
        {
          "key": "processing_tutorial_complete",
          "value": {
            "speakerName": "Ruben",
            "text": "You've got the basics. Now you can debone your own catch.\n\nProcessed fish sell for twice the price. It's worth the effort.\n\n(Achievement Unlocked: Processor's Apprentice)",
            "showAsAction": true,
            "showConditions": [],
            "triggersOnShow": [
              "CompleteQuest:PROCESSING_TUTORIAL",
              "UnlockAchievement:Processor's Apprentice",
              "SetSkill:Processing:1"
            ],
            "choices": [
              {
                "choiceText": "Thank you for teaching me.",
                "resultDialogId": "post_tutorial_qa",
                "triggersOnShow": [],
                "showConditions": []
              }
            ],
            "nextDialogId": ""
          }
        },
        {
          "key": "post_tutorial_qa",
          "value": {
            "speakerName": "Ruben",
            "text": "Is there a point of technique you wish to clarify?\n\nOr are you ready to process your own catch?",
            "showAsAction": true,
            "showConditions": [
              {
                "conditionType": 3,
                "conditionKey": "PROCESSING_TUTORIAL",
                "conditionValue": "COMPLETED"
              }
            ],
            "triggersOnShow": [],
            "choices": [
              {
                "choiceText": "I want to process my fish.",
                "resultDialogId": "",
                "triggersOnChoose": ["RecordFishProcessed:1", "CompleteQuest:ART_OF_VALUE_4", "LoadScene:DeboningMainScene", "PlayMusic:DeboningBGM"],
                "showConditions": []
              },
              {
                "choiceText": "What's the most important rule in processing?",
                "resultDialogId": "qa_rule",
                "triggersOnShow": [],
                "showConditions": []
              },
              {
                "choiceText": "Can you tell me more about getting better tools?",
                "resultDialogId": "qa_tools",
                "triggersOnShow": [],
                "showConditions": []
              },
              {
                "choiceText": "Any final advice before I start on my own?",
                "resultDialogId": "qa_advice",
                "triggersOnShow": [],
                "showConditions": []
              },
              {
                "choiceText": "Thanks, that's all I needed.",
                "resultDialogId": "qa_end",
                "triggersOnShow": [],
                "showConditions": []
              }
            ],
            "nextDialogId": ""
          }
        },
        {
          "key": "qa_rule",
          "value": {
            "speakerName": "Ruben",
            "text": "Respect the life that was given.\n\nEvery cut should be purposeful, every part considered.\n\nThis isn't just business; it's a form of stewardship.",
            "showAsAction": true,
            "showConditions": [],
            "triggersOnShow": [],
            "choices": [
              {
                "choiceText": "What else should I know?",
                "resultDialogId": "post_tutorial_qa",
                "triggersOnShow": [],
                "showConditions": []
              }
            ],
            "nextDialogId": ""
          }
        },
        {
          "key": "qa_tools",
          "value": {
            "speakerName": "Ruben",
            "text": "Focus on skill first. Tools come later.\n\nWhen you're ready, Soria at Local Galore may have a Processor's Starter Kit.\n\nA master with a simple knife is better than a novice with a golden one.",
            "showAsAction": true,
            "showConditions": [],
            "triggersOnShow": [],
            "choices": [
              {
                "choiceText": "What else should I know?",
                "resultDialogId": "post_tutorial_qa",
                "triggersOnShow": [],
                "showConditions": []
              }
            ],
            "nextDialogId": ""
          }
        },
        {
          "key": "qa_advice",
          "value": {
            "speakerName": "Ruben",
            "text": "Start with what you know—your tilapia or mackerel.\n\nKeep your technique precise. A careless cut is wasteful.\n\nRemember: the better you care for your craft, the better you honor the catch.",
            "showAsAction": true,
            "showConditions": [],
            "triggersOnShow": [],
            "choices": [
              {
                "choiceText": "What else should I know?",
                "resultDialogId": "post_tutorial_qa",
                "triggersOnShow": [],
                "showConditions": []
              }
            ],
            "nextDialogId": ""
          }
        },
        {
          "key": "qa_end",
          "value": {
            "speakerName": "Ruben",
            "text": "The queue is waiting. But so is your future.\n\nUse what you've learned. And remember: the knife reveals character.\n\nWhat kind of steward will yours show you to be?",
            "showConditions": [],
            "triggersOnShow": [],
            "choices": [],
            "nextDialogId": ""
          }
        },
